sentences.content: The following exercises allow me to fill in the prompts given the corresponding response lists in increasingly more difficult ordering until no response list is shown.
She woke and got out of [_bed_].
After she got up, she put on her [_clothes_].
We sit with her at the [_table_].
The car is running out of [_gas_].
Can I put your call on [_hold_].
He is not in now, please call back [_later_].
